Istio Gateway:
-------------
- LB that sits in edge of mesh instead fo k8s ingress
- Istio ingress gateway managed inbound traffic and 
- Istio egress gateway managed inbound traffic and 
- Ingress gateway deployed usong envoy proxy

Virtual services:
------------------
- They define a set of routing rules from ingress gateway into the service mesh

- Traffic for one or more hostname
- Diff version of service
- Support standard and regex path


